{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>YAARRGH! Battle Island!</strong><i> is a 3D Procedural Generated Pirate Fantasy battle arena game,</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612750/extras/RumbleBI.png?t=1733108034\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Within an Island belonging to a sweet little fairy overrun by skeleton hordes. Players will need to work together to defend the fairy to save the Island from the undead armies, you will be faced with wave after wave of skeletons and their king. Once the king has been defeated, the Island will be saved, winning the fairy\u2019s favour including three wishes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612750/extras/CallToAction.gif?t=1733108034\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Smooth terrain with smooth blending textures creating a beautiful Island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stylized 3D models with bright fresh textures to bring characters alive &amp; toony particle effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A new YAARRGH pirate melee system with a strong emphasis on skill-based combat &amp; added cartoonish humour.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612750/extras/Explosion.gif?t=1733108034\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>MULTIPLAYER:</i></strong> Private or public servers. Create a local private server for you and your friends, or host a public server for anyone to join.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>COOP:</i></strong> Objective team base gameplay, defending and defeating waves of Ai with your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>MINE:</i></strong> Dig for treasure or mine for ores. Find many types of rocks to be smelted into ingots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>BUILD:</i></strong> Block building construction \u2013 Design and build houses, towers, fortresses or underground bunkers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>CRAFT:</i></strong> Create weapons, armor and animations that you will need to survive. With many types of resources and materials available.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Development</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We are working on new content in 2024, fixing bugs, and testing new features, join us to get access to <strong>YAARRGH! Battle Island!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612750/extras/vlcsnap-2021-03-07-17h22m18s328.png?t=1733108034\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our game development is going strong before release, you can check out our progress by following us on YouTube.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1612750?t=1733108034","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612750/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1733108034","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612750/89013cb6615ed9b1bf3aa7ee241962ce3397d2d3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733108034","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612750/89013cb6615ed9b1bf3aa7ee241962ce3397d2d3/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733108034","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"descrip